{"tid":1197554,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"迪列治：C.朗拿度邀請我去祖記 我一開始有點驚訝","createTime":"2019-06-10T04:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T01:00:41.000Z","uid":173952,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1b5995e1c80c468145205830a3e1ca2b2bf7c8ef","tid":1197554,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:13:30.000Z","msg":"歐國聯決賽中葡萄牙1-0戰勝荷蘭奪得首屆冠軍。賽後，據荷蘭媒體《NOS》報導，迪列治透露C.朗拿度邀請他加盟祖記。<br />\n<br />\n  「C.朗拿度邀請我去祖記。我對他的問題感到驚訝，這也是為什麼我笑了一下，我一開始沒理解他的問題。」<br />\n<br />\n  迪列治表示會好好思考後決定自己的未來，據此前媒體報導，曼聯已經退出了爭奪，現在巴塞、祖記和巴黎在競爭他。不知道C.朗拿度的親自遊說是否會影響他的決定。"},{"pid":"4b1c829ff6f3484fadff58ae47e14978204f90a2","tid":1197554,"uid":4957,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:14:41.000Z","msg":"牙朗做埋球探<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84026dda80c31b9ad6e6ad9432b968b5817c9c59","tid":1197554,"uid":1423,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:15:56.000Z","msg":"講不出說話"},{"pid":"39414097a33b55cda03403e1314485677d0be65b","tid":1197554,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:18:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd75b0ee66861c53494836ee267b1e76798c700","tid":1197554,"uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:57:04.000Z","msg":"做埋引援"},{"pid":"d74b921a6c87955d7e338c467c267c69df53337a","tid":1197554,"uid":43785,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:59:03.000Z","msg":"同迪莊去巴啦"},{"pid":"d54891e798506595b6e1b3a632c3e1cc1de86718","tid":1197554,"uid":34571,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:00:56.000Z","msg":"蛆仲有錢咩"},{"pid":"02607d92b5ab571809a899e0b18018be761c763e","tid":1197554,"uid":58630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:01:43.000Z","msg":"是否很驚訝～"},{"pid":"c337551c558079ae47a8792d2af85425d6f95189","tid":1197554,"ui